title: Report: Henry Ruggs III driving 156 mph before deadly Las Vegas crash
author: KTNV Channel 13 Las Vegas
description: Henry Ruggs III appeared in a Las Vegas courtroom Wednesday morning after a deadly crash occurred in west Las Vegas on Tuesday.
